306
00:21:12,793 --> 00:21:16,388
I had no idea you might be grappling
with personal issues.

307
00:21:16,717 --> 00:21:19,675
Some psychiatrist, huh?

308
00:21:19,974 --> 00:21:23,853
The truth is i came down here
to try to talk you into going out with me.

309
00:21:24,232 --> 00:21:27,030
I guess it's still a pretty bad idea.

310
00:21:27,322 --> 00:21:29,438
You're being so honest with me.

311
00:21:29,701 --> 00:21:33,296
That is such
an attractive quality in a man.

312
00:21:37,634 --> 00:21:41,752
Well, you know,
